{"tid":2024353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「限時限量」國際戰線要人！有錢分啦喂","createTime":"2020-05-19T14:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T16:47:33.000Z","uid":142429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"44ef532d8e5bb1927873d1b0843af18936291907","tid":2024353,"uid":142429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"係去<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Twitter</span></strong></strong></span></strong> <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搶like同retweet</span></strong></span>呀！<br />\n<br />\n依排鋪頭生意好好，希望攞少少錢出黎鼓勵大家做國際戰線。Sir This Way不單單只係口號，係需要大家既支持同推廣先可以令美國，甚至全世界有大義之名去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">清算</span></span>港共班走狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要大家將少少睇Facebook, Instagram, WhatsApp既時間去Twitter到like同retweet，我相信Sir This Way不是夢！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">廿三條近了，<br />\n唔好放棄任何發聲既機會！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n符合以下<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極容易</span></span></strong>條件，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">當日將捐一千港元到612基金/星火，直至2020年6月9日</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7vkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=b802f6c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nTwitter Bot 中的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全部置頂任務</span></span></strong>（包括task 1-task4)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Retweets 數目超過3,000<br />\n2. Likes 數目超過3,000<br />\n3. 「Optional」各項每多3,000 我當日再捐多1,000港元</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S 要接受當日cap圖為準（post圖）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎大家黎「搶」我錢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星星之火可以燎原，希望可以拋磚引玉！<br />\n<br />\n香港人爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5794e00b844e49fe2ce179a0b74b815260f653f1","tid":2024353,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:27:40.000Z","msg":"問心 大家想唔想香港獨立建國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cd1b40e30bbed0a63f30df52d996262d715f33f1","tid":2024353,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:28:00.000Z","msg":"我地抗爭要成功 首要改變返我地套mindset<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2